<h4 id="_2-1-mybatis介绍" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-1-mybatis介绍" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2.1 MyBatis介绍</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p>MyBatisPlus（简称MP）是基于MyBatis框架基础上开发的增强型工具，旨在简化开发、提高效率</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>官网：<a href="https://mybatis.plus/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https<ExternalLinkIcon/></a><a href="https://mybatis.plus/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">😕/mybatis.plus<ExternalLinkIcon/></a><a href="https://mybatis.plus/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">/<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>   <a href="https://mp.baomidou.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://mp.baomidou.com<ExternalLinkIcon/></a><a href="https://mp.baomidou.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">/<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="_2-2-mybatisplus特性" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-2-mybatisplus特性" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2.2 MyBatisPlus特性</h4>
<ul>
<li>无侵入：只做增强不做改变，不会对现有工程产生影响</li>
<li>强大的 CRUD 操作：内置通用 Mapper，少量配置即可实现单表CRUD 操作</li>
<li>支持 Lambda：编写查询条件无需担心字段写错</li>
<li>支持主键自动生成</li>
<li>内置分页插件</li>
<li>……</li>
</ul>
